thread.title: Emmerdale

author: Fiona Flynn
title: Emmerdale
text: This whole Ross trying to kill Pete thing is getting old at this stage but they're at it again this week as Ross knocks his brother out with a baseball bat tonight when he arrives at the caravan. Just what does he have planned for him this time? Meanwhile, Robert is intrigued when he hears that Bernice has moved into Home Farm, knowing this could be useful to him. Never misses an opportunity, that Robert.
